name: "Ice Cube, South Central Los Angeles, 1991" by NORMSKI (Photograph/Print)
description:
Ice Cube, posing next to his Chevy Tracker Jeep, outside his mother's house, South Central Los Angeles, 1991

Taken by legendary UK street style photographer NORMSKI.

- Embossed & signed by Normski. 
- Printed on 200gsm matt stock.
- Measures 420mm x 297mm (A3)
- Print comes rolled in tissue paper in a card tube.

As seen on the recent range of t-shirts released by Classic Material, Normski and Footpatrol
